Collection of Paul Betz. ALS;
                  4p. (A copy in another hand is in Bodleian Library, MS Eng. Lett. c. 25. TR;
                  3p.) Endorsement: Keswick 10 Sepr. 1816 .  Previously  published:
                  Kenneth Curry (ed.), New Letters of Robert Southey, 2 vols (London
                  and New York, 1965), II, pp. 141–144.  Note on MS: the letter was originally
                  an enclosure in Southey to Bedford on 10 September 1816, see Letter 2838.
